name: Nite Ize CamJam Cord Tightener (2 Pack)
description: Tighten lines without gnarliness or knots. Clip the carabiner to a tarp grommet or a bear bag for a tensioned guyline. Tie a loop in the opposite end, clip it to the carabiner, and you’ve got an adjustable tie-down to attach gear to a pack, rack, or boat deck. The cord locks securely on a tensioned line and releases easily.Cam is made of durable plastic. Carabiner gate is stainless steel.Fits rope sizes: 2-5mm.Dimensions are 67 x 35 x 15mm.Includes 3.1m (5mm) rope.Sold in pack of 2.Note: not for use where failure could result in bodily injury or property damage. Not for climbing.
